%N A390029 Triangle read by rows: T(n,k) = Sum_{j=0..2k} (-1)^j * binomial(2k,j) * (2+k-j)^(2n).
%H A390029 Donald E. Knuth, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/math/9207222">Johann Faulhaber and Sums of Powers</a>, arXiv:9207222 [math.CA], 1992.
%H A390029 Petro Kolosov, <a href="https://github.com/kolosovpetro/SumsOfPowersViaCentralFiniteDifferencesAndNewtonFormula/tree/main/mathematica">Mathematica programs</a>, GitHub, 2026.
